{"tid":2369133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（武肺疫苗）香港僅 27% 受訪者對中國疫苗表示正面","createTime":"2021-01-17T00:17:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T02:46:05.000Z","uid":36494,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"97c0445d919cd49ec5998a2b92876c9ffe3b0c47","tid":2369133,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T00:17:19.000Z","msg":"民調機構亦問各國受訪者，對不同國家所製造疫苗的態度。結果顯示，香港人對德國製造的疫苗最有好感，有六成人稱對疫苗「更為正面」；中國製造的疫苗方面，香港僅 27% 受訪者對其表示正面，反之負面的有 47%。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他國家對中國製疫苗的態度亦偏向負面，其中丹麥僅 4% 受訪者稱對中國疫苗感到「更為正面」，「更為負面」的則有 57%。反觀中國受訪者對自己國家製造的疫苗更有信心，有 85% 人表示正面，負面的僅得 2%。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OwYaHOD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOwYaHOD.jpg&h=940de3f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E8%B7%A8%E5%9C%8B%E6%B0%91%E8%AA%BF-%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%B0%91%E7%9C%BE%E6%9C%80%E5%82%BE%E5%90%91%E6%8E%A5%E7%A8%AE%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%8E%92%E5%B0%BE%E4%B8%89/?fbclid=IwAR3eohYFQ4bcKIdtWETBen0wR-JHLx_-J_tOTptzHfOJdvRxF7sLx0dyrmo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E8%25B7%25A8%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25AA%25BF-%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%259C%25BE%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%2582%25BE%25E5%2590%2591%25E6%258E%25A5%25E7%25A8%25AE%25E7%2596%25AB%25E8%258B%2597-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%258E%2592%25E5%25B0%25BE%25E4%25B8%2589%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3eohYFQ4bcKIdtWETBen0wR-JHLx_-J_tOTptzHfOJdvRxF7sLx0dyrmo&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHJE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=8d656918\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E8%25B7%25A8%25E5%25